n附表：\r\n編號 竊得物品即犯罪所得 數量 1 排氣管含氧感知器 1組 2 觸媒 1組 3 觸媒墊片 1組","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e6%98%93%2c440%2c20220329%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,易,440,20220329,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"易","JNO":"440","JDATE":"20220329","JTITLE":"加重竊盜"}